.TH VAF-SUB 8 "2026-06-10" "versatile-autoreg-vaf" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
vaf-sub \- VAF sub-instance federation loop
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vaf-sub
.I name
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vaf-sub
runs the full
.BR vaf (8)
main loop for a named sub-instance defined under
.IR /etc/vaf/vaf.sub/<name>/ .
It inherits the base configuration from
.I /etc/vaf/vaf.conf
and overrides federation-specific variables
.RB ( UPPER_VAS_HOST ", " KEY )
from
.IR /etc/vaf/vaf.sub/<name>/vaf.conf .
.PP
.B vaf-sub
is not intended to be invoked directly. It is started and supervised by
.BR vaf-sub-manager (8),
which is in turn launched by
.BR vaf (8)
when
.B PARALLEL_MODE
is
.B both
or
.BR only_parallel .
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vaf (8),
.BR vaf-sub-manager (8),
.BR vaf-sub-instance (8)
.SH AUTHOR
Gabriel Navia <correos@gabrielnav.es>
